lead_paragraph: Cable matched her career-high with 25 points and grabbed seven rebounds to lead No. 3 Notre Dame to an 82-46 victory over North Carolina State on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Cable Scores 25, No. 3 Notre Dame Defeats NC State 82-46
